thread.title: Greek minister says 'No' boosts government in credit talks
thread.title_full: Greek minister says 'No' boosts government in credit talks | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Greek minister says 'No' boosts government in credit talks
text:
ATHENS, July 5 Greece's rejection of creditors's proposals in a referendum on Sunday boosts the government's negotiating position in talks with lenders, Labour Minister Panos Skourletis said.
"The government now has a strong negotiating tool to bring about a deal which will open a new path for us," Skourletis told reporters. (Reporting By Michele Kambas)
